reviews.review_text: Best Aud source? This sounds great.  Like really great.  So does the BK4011 pull.  After listening back n forth, over n over, between the 2, I am going to go with this Brotman Schps source.  That BnK is sweet though. Check it out for sure, compare to the Brotman.
